Description: Provides fixture projects and ground-truth datasets for
    benchmarking the rrlmgraph package.  Fixtures range from a minimal
    data-science script project to a medium-sized Shiny application and a
    small R package, covering the full spectrum of project types supported
    by rrlmgraph.
